text: I have a suggestion which I am not sure where to post, and apologies if it is a dupe: I think new users would benefit from an extra "Info" statement related to precompile when you work from the interpreter. Something that either estimates the time (even giving a vague sense of what is normal) or gives a suggestion on how to work around it.
